def bingo(ticket, win):
    return 'Winner!' if sum(chr(n) in s for s, n in ticket) >= win else 'Loser!'

def bingo(ticket, win):
    return "Winner!" if sum( w in map(ord, s) for s, w in ticket ) >= win else "Loser!"

def bingo(ticket,win):
    return "Loser!" if sum(1 if chr(i[1]) in i[0] else 0 for i in ticket)<win else "Winner!"

def bingo(ticket,win):
    return 'Winner!' if sum(chr(arr[1]) in arr[0] for arr in ticket)>=win else 'Loser!'

    return 'WLionsneerr!!'[sum(chr(n)in s for s,n in ticket)<win::2]
